01:07:16,961 --> 01:07:19,557
Get up there!
Everybody, up there!

529
01:07:19,641 --> 01:07:20,877
(men shouting)

530
01:07:21,950 --> 01:07:23,599
Come on men! Agh!

531
01:07:33,495 --> 01:07:37,614
(screams)

532
01:07:39,431 --> 01:07:41,285
Get him, down there!

533
01:07:47,471 --> 01:07:48,831
Get down.

534
01:07:49,945 --> 01:07:51,344
(Colonel) Shoot them!

535
01:08:10,394 --> 01:08:11,920
Ah!

536
01:08:12,003 --> 01:08:13,980
(men shouting indistinctly)

537
01:08:35,419 --> 01:08:36,946
Okay, let's get out of here.

538
01:08:45,358 --> 01:08:46,635
Shoot them!

539
01:08:50,016 --> 01:08:51,416
Shit.

540
01:08:51,500 --> 01:08:54,138
(man) Dynamite!
Run for your lives!

541
01:08:54,221 --> 01:08:56,487
Take cover!

542
01:08:59,417 --> 01:09:02,300
Ya-hoo!

543
01:09:45,346 --> 01:09:47,240
Shit! We did it!

544
01:09:47,324 --> 01:09:49,180
(all cheer)

545
01:09:49,263 --> 01:09:50,499
(gunshot, all gasp)

546
01:09:50,583 --> 01:09:51,982
They hit Jacques!

547
01:09:55,200 --> 01:09:57,384
Come on!
Back to town!

548
01:09:57,467 --> 01:09:59,321
(indistinct shouting)

549
01:09:59,405 --> 01:10:00,971
Come on.
(gunshots)

550
01:10:03,363 --> 01:10:06,618
Let's close this damn circus down!
Burn it!

551
01:10:06,702 --> 01:10:09,259
(screaming)

552
01:10:09,342 --> 01:10:10,371
Come on!

553
01:11:04,176 --> 01:11:07,722
(rifle cocks)

554
01:11:07,804 --> 01:11:09,370
(gunshot, crow caws)

555
01:11:14,401 --> 01:11:15,597
Kill.

556
01:11:34,439 --> 01:11:35,716
Run.

557
01:11:56,704 --> 01:11:59,711
Hey, come on!
Into the hotel!

558
01:11:59,795 --> 01:12:01,072
Keep low!

559
01:12:01,155 --> 01:12:04,577
(men screaming)

560
01:12:13,111 --> 01:12:14,306
Get them!

561
01:13:39,117 --> 01:13:40,601
(indistinct shouting and gunfire)

562
01:14:28,757 --> 01:14:31,066
Here! Take her!

563
01:14:36,550 --> 01:14:37,621
Skinny!

564
01:14:47,146 --> 01:14:51,061
(gunshots, April cries)

565
01:14:51,145 --> 01:14:53,865
(Eight-Ball wheezing and grunting)

566
01:15:03,391 --> 01:15:06,399
I-I couldn't protect April.

567
01:15:17,533 --> 01:15:19,922
(April crying in distance)

568
01:15:24,004 --> 01:15:25,859
Guard the hallway!

569
01:15:25,942 --> 01:15:28,458
And don't let a damn soul
into this room!

570
01:15:34,436 --> 01:15:36,498
(distant gunfire)

571
01:15:54,762 --> 01:15:57,853
(sword tip dragging)

572
01:16:12,449 --> 01:16:13,974
What the...

573
01:16:15,954 --> 01:16:17,973
(chokes and sputters)

574
01:16:40,115 --> 01:16:41,143
Agh!

575
01:16:42,588 --> 01:16:44,195
(sword tip dragging)

576
01:16:57,430 --> 01:17:00,029
One more step,
and she's soup.

577
01:17:01,471 --> 01:17:03,902
I said stop!

578
01:17:49,051 --> 01:17:50,821
(both grunting)

579
01:18:55,017 --> 01:18:56,128
Yah!

580
01:18:56,212 --> 01:18:58,396
Agh!

581
01:19:00,790 --> 01:19:03,592
That sure is a purty scar
I gave you.

582
01:19:09,819 --> 01:19:11,591
Agh! Ooh!

583
01:19:13,159 --> 01:19:14,724
Ooh! Ugh!

584
01:19:47,295 --> 01:19:51,541
I'll see you in Hell, little girl.
(chuckles)

585
01:19:51,625 --> 01:19:55,500
Wear something nasty.
(laughs)

586
01:19:55,584 --> 01:19:56,903
Yaah!

587
01:20:28,319 --> 01:20:31,410
Is this the new life
you have found?

588
01:20:34,505 --> 01:20:36,029
Funny.

589
01:20:36,112 --> 01:20:39,203
Look much like the old one.

590
01:20:45,718 --> 01:20:50,665
Do you think you will tell her
that you kill her mother,

591
01:20:50,749 --> 01:20:55,819
her father and her entire clan?

592
01:20:57,757 --> 01:21:00,148
She is the enemy.

593
01:21:00,232 --> 01:21:05,260
She will always be the enemy.

594
01:21:05,343 --> 01:21:10,950
You came to me to be strong.

595
01:21:11,033 --> 01:21:14,950
I have made you the strongest.

596
01:21:17,918 --> 01:21:20,392
Kill her now.

597
01:21:20,475 --> 01:21:25,092
You do not belong here.

598
01:21:25,175 --> 01:21:26,494
I do.

599
01:21:29,379 --> 01:21:31,276
I did.

600
01:23:17,485 --> 01:23:21,524
You have the perfect body
for an assassin

601
01:23:21,607 --> 01:23:23,503
but the heart of a priest.

602
01:23:32,821 --> 01:23:35,543
Your heart will become
your biggest enemy.

603
01:23:50,674 --> 01:23:53,848
You must kill your biggest enemy.

604
01:23:53,932 --> 01:23:56,076
We are assassins.

605
01:23:56,159 --> 01:23:59,991
All that we love,
we will destroy.

606
01:24:21,638 --> 01:24:24,441
You are assassin.

607
01:24:24,523 --> 01:24:29,057
All that you love,
you'll destroy.

608
01:26:33,695 --> 01:26:35,632
Did we win?

609
01:26:35,715 --> 01:26:38,436
We survived.

610
01:26:38,519 --> 01:26:40,167
Some of us.

611
01:26:42,561 --> 01:26:46,022
I'm not goin' with you.
Am I?

612
01:27:38,838 --> 01:27:42,258
I guess that's the end ofthem.

613
01:27:42,342 --> 01:27:43,496
No.

614
01:27:43,579 --> 01:27:46,258
It is just the beginning.

615
01:27:46,342 --> 01:27:49,599
What about the baby?
She gonna be safe?

616
01:27:49,682 --> 01:27:53,845
They are listening for this to cry.

617
01:27:55,907 --> 01:27:57,554
Not her.

618
01:28:11,945 --> 01:28:14,830
That's right, Sand Man.

619
01:28:14,913 --> 01:28:16,645
Keep walkin'.

620
01:28:22,500 --> 01:28:25,180
The warrior walked away.

621
01:28:25,263 --> 01:28:27,940
And legend has it,
he never stopped walkin',

622
01:28:28,024 --> 01:28:32,929
always making sure to keep
as much distance as possible

623
01:28:33,012 --> 01:28:37,961
between himself
and the little gal he loved.

624
01:29:09,007 --> 01:29:11,314
(woman singing operatically)

625
01:29:21,707 --> 01:29:22,982
How much?

626
01:29:32,549 --> 01:29:34,198
Free.

627
01:29:35,243 --> 01:29:38,373
(singing continues)

